{
  "stem": "13556.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is engineers and lawyers and doctors and teachers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was over there, like a-- this, this is the place where they, they give them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To tell you the truth, in the beginning, when I finished the school, I was finished-- I finished the best, top student.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sure they will accept me like an excellent worker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came to Israel and they take me for a test, I couldn't pass the test or show demand and high, high qualification, which I was very disappointed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I finished with 5-plus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me I am excellent-- not good, just excellent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Israel, they give me a test, and I couldn't pass.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they give me the lowest grade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then it's OK, I think already for the lowest grade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I realized where I'm going to work is welding boilers, and the boilers under high pressure.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was not prepared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't learn this kind of stuff to do it, just straight weldings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and I was welding over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working in a shop, [NON-ENGLISH], in, in Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they laid me off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When you're over 28, 29, they don't want to-- older people in this time to hold it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they're holding you a year, they're obligated to hold you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They can't fire you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but to fire you, to lay you off, they have to pay you lots of money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's they-- they hold me for 11 months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they let me home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they asked me to come after a week back to work, back from the-- from the-- from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I decided not to go to them anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was disappointed.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
